messages.subject: Help!  I can't keep up!
messages.msgSnippet: This list is so high traffic that I can t keep up! I really love this list, but after not checking all day there were 104 messages!  Yikes, I miss so much. Is
messages.messageBody:
This list is so high traffic that I can't keep up!
I really love this list, but after not checking all day there were 104
messages! Yikes, I miss so much.
Is there something to be done?
Just wondering since I did unsub for a bit, but missed the like minded
people.
Ann
